                            <comment id="369813" author="adilger" created="Tue, 18 Apr 2023 17:26:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It turns out this is because SLES15 no longer installs &quot;&lt;tt&gt;netstat&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; by default. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
